.TH GLwDrawingAreaSwapBuffers 3X "" "" "" ""
.SH NAME
\fBGLwDrawingAreaSwapBuffers \(em swap buffers in a GLwDrawingArea.\fP
.iX "GLwDrawingAreaSwapBuffers"
.iX "GLwDrawingArea"
.sp 1
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fB#include <X11/GLw/GLwDraw.h>\fP
.br
\fBvoid GLwDrawingAreaSwapBuffers(w)\fP
.br
.ta .5i 1.5i
	Widget \fIw\fP;
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBGLwDrawingAreaSwapBuffers\fP is a front end to \fIglXSwapBuffers\fP,
however instead of passing in a Display and a Window, a Widget is
passed in.
.SH RELATED INFORMATION
\fBGLwMDrawingArea\fP, \fBglXSwapBuffers\fP.
